verbose_text: Since DOC2A has been reported as a suppressor gene in many carcinomas such as colorectal cancer and urothelial cancer [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR], we suggest AHR might promote glioma progression through inhibiting the tumor suppressor gene, DOC2A.
